  "description": "<p>并非所有的酒店都配备最前沿的技术产品。旅行者面对牛速的室内Wi-Fi，过时的台式电脑和根本找不到要看频道的电视都会抓狂。根据2012 Hotels.com调查显示，34%的客人认为选择酒店最先考虑的该是免费Wi-Fi，对于商务旅行者而言，比例增加到56%。然而无线上网只是冰山一角。<strong>一些酒店现在提供极好的附加设备，比如通过RFID实现房间自动化，免费提供智能手机和苹果设备等。一起去看看北美十家高科技程度最为发达的酒店吧。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e6292ca/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243939.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%8C%97%E7%BE%8E%E5%8D%81%E5%A4%A7%E9%AB%98%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243939.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%8C%97%E7%BE%8E%E5%8D%81%E5%A4%A7%E9%AB%98%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243939.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%8C%97%E7%BE%8E%E5%8D%81%E5%A4%A7%E9%AB%98%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243939.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%8C%97%E7%BE%8E%E5%8D%81%E5%A4%A7%E9%AB%98%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243939.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%8C%97%E7%BE%8E%E5%8D%81%E5%A4%A7%E9%AB%98%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/em